comments: The play originates outside the LDB. Tucker (PHI) is the secondary defender and does not establish a legal guarding position outside of the RA and extends his hand forward into an airborne Morant (MEM), which affects his driving shot attempt.
Embiid (PHI) makes incidental hand on ball contact with Jackson Jr. (MEM) as they pursue the rebound.
Harden (PHI) cleanly dislodges the ball from Bane (MEM) during his drive.
Harden's (PHI) right foot remains inbounds as his heel does not come down on the sideline.
Tucker (PHI) is in the paint for less than three seconds when he moves to imminently guard Morant (MEM).
Tucker (PHI) establishes a legal guarding position in Morant's (MEM) path before his upward motion and absorbs contact when it occurs.
Embiid (PHI) makes clean contact with the ball, dislodging the shot from Morant's (MEM) control.
Tucker (PHI) swipes down and initiates contact with Tillman's (MEM) right wrist, which affects his play at the basket.
Embiid (PHI) extends his forearm into Jackson Jr.'s (MEM) side, which impedes his ability to pursue the rebound.
Harden (PHI) and Brooks (MEM) engage and disengage off-ball as Harden reaches for the inbounds pass.
Tillman (MEM) moves alongside Harden's (PHI) path and marginal body contact occurs during the driving shot attempt.
Brooks (MEM) maintains verticality and absorbs the contact that occurs during Harden's (PHI) driving shot attempt.
Embiid (PHI) and Tillman (MEM) engage in marginal hand to hand contact during the rebound.
Harris (PHI) momentarily rests a forearm on Morant's (MEM) side before retracting it and marginal contact occurs during the driving shot attempt.
Morant (MEM) and Harden (PHI) come together in pursuit of the loose ball and marginal contact occurs as they go to the ground.
Jackson Jr. (MEM) establishes himself in McDaniels' (PHI) path and does not deliver illegal contact.
Jackson Jr. (MEM) comes through Harris' (PHI) right arm to tie the ball up.
All Technical Fouls are reviewed by League Operations
All Technical Fouls are reviewed by League Operations
Harden (PHI) makes contact with the ball and dislodges it prior to incidental hand contact occurring thereafter with Brooks (MEM) during his jump shot attempt.
